title: Minecraft transforms Westlake, Strongsville movie theaters into gaming arenas (photos)
text:
Published By: Cleveland.com: Westlake - Today 
The first-ever Minecraft fall gaming leagues will begin Oct. 6 and 7 in Westlake and Strongsville....
